N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 13 ยง 52.1 - Scope of part

State Regulations

This Part shall govern the conduct of hearings held by the Securities Bureau of the

Department of Law pursuant to chapter 325, Laws of 1965; the New York Theatre Ticket Distribution Act, and as amended from time to
time. Notes
